data.description: Don't miss this opportunity to own this Gorgeous 1 year old home located in the highly desirable District 1! This Property sits on 3/4 acre lot and boasts 4BR/3 Baths with a Bonus Room. Home offers open floor plan, White Custom shaker cabinets, granite tops, pantry, tile backsplash, Black SS Appliances, Large Island, laminate flooring throughout the living area. Large dining area, lots of picture windows for natural light. Master suite, judges panel, sitting room, double vanities, walk-in closet, tiled shower and a separate tub. Upstairs you will find a Bonus Room with a full bath. Enjoy the covered Deck and privacy offered to the back yard with one side of the property bordered by a thick tree line. Plenty of storage in the extra tall crawl space. A side gravel drive offers the perfect place to store a boat, RV, or extra parking. This home is sure to impress. Call today to schedule your private showing.
